- "top 10 most popular artists in each country" refers to the top 10 artists ranked by their popularity score within their country;
- "fan base" refers to the number of followers an artist has;
- "emotional resonance of their music" is represented by the average sentiment score of the lyrics;
- "number of times their tracks have been played" refers to the total play count of their tracks;
- "feedback from their audience" includes the count of user feedback and the average sentiment score from user feedback.
